headline: 2 Industrials Stocks with Exciting Potential and 1 to Brush Off
summary: Whether you see them or not, industrials businesses play a crucial part in our daily activities. Still, their generally high capital requirements expose them to the ups and downs of economic cycles, and the market seems to be baking in a prolonged downturn as the industry has shed 12.1% over the past six months. This performance was worse than the S&P 500’s 2.4% fall.
